	Motor control centre manufacturer Shaw Controls, a Zest WEG group company, is now a proud ISO 9000:2015 certified local manufacturing facility. Shannon de Ryhove has the story. Shannon de Ryhove:
	ISO 9000:2015 describes the fundamental concepts and principles of quality management which are applicable to both organisations and customers. This is especially true for those customers seeking confidence in Shaw Control’s ability to consistently provide products and services conforming to their customer’s requirements. Zest WEG group CEO Louis Meiring: Shannon de Ryhove:
	Shaw Controls is focused not only on providing world class electrical solutions. It now also has the necessary skills and expertise to manufacture electrical and control panels for all types of applications under strict health and safety parameters with the certification of IEC 61641 specifications. Zest WEG group CEO Louis Meiring: Sashnee Moodley:
